Local Integer INDIC : INDIC = indice
Raz mkstat
Call TITADI(GBOUT1,"909") From TRTDIV
Call TEXTE(6028,GBOUTS) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(12276,GBOUTP) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(16134,GBOUTA) From OBJDIV
Onkey 129 Titled GBOUT1 Call B1_LEG(zc) From W1HRLIC1
Onkey   2 Titled GBOUTS Call S_LEG(zc) From W1HRLIC1
Onkey 144 Titled GBOUTP Call P_LEG(zc) From W1HRLIC1
Onkey 146 Titled GBOUTA Call SA_LEG(zc) From W1HRLIC1
Gosub _AFF
